  "body": "<p>Here are two for you since I neglected to post the one from last week on the blog, although it did appear on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/amytangerine/\">Instagram</a>. That and <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/amytangerine?sub_confirmation=1\">YouTube</a> seem to be more my jam lately, but I am prioritizing this blog as I have a lot of cool stuff to share with you.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595976013492-JFZH1R3UA63YYEV248RC/image-asset.png\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595976039493-7WRMQXJ3UEQALXSZ9FCC/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Thanks to Sian who shared the Kurt Vonnegut quote with me in the comments from a couple weeks ago!</p><p>I'm using <a href=\"http://goo.gl/b9K6TP\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a> and I have finally tried a waterbrush and found <a href=\"http://goo.gl/eDsF0u\">one that I love by Tim Holtz/Ranger</a>. If you have a favorite quote – silly, snarky or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}